&gt; If people felt that men and women are truly equal organisms, then the way to approach sports should be no different than to approach other jobs. Co-ed sports would allow the best participants to rise to the top. 

&amp;#x200B;

Women can play in any of the four major sports. There just hasn't been a female who can compete better than their male counterparts in the major four sports. 

&amp;#x200B;

No one is denying that there are biological differences based on someone's sex. I've genuinely never heard someone claim that in good faith. 

&amp;#x200B;

When people talk about gender equality they're talking about an individuals position in society. Providing equal opportunity to people regardless of their sex.

&amp;#x200B;
